  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Ludovisi Palace offers an extensive breakfast buffet with cold cuts, cheeses, a selection of hot items such as, scrambled eggs, bacon and sausages. Cakes and pastries are also available along with hot and cold beverages. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
