  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Double Rooms </strong>are about 14m² and are decorated in a modern style with wooden furnishings. These rooms have a queen size bed. All rooms are equipped with modern amenities including, air conditioning, minibar, alarm clock, WiFi, private bathroom and WC, LCD TV, safe, a hairdryer and a daily newspaper. These accommodate up to 2 adults and a child (baby cot free of charge, available on request). </p>
<p><strong>Classic Triple Rooms </strong>are about 18m² and have a double queen sized bed and a single bed. They sleep 3 people and are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> are larger at about 17m² and have a double queen sized bed or twin beds. These rooms accommodate up to 2 adults and a child (baby cot free of charge, available on request). These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Triple Rooms</strong> sleep up to 3 people and are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Executive Double Rooms</strong>  are a spacious at about 32m² and have an extra large double bed. They are located on the higher floors of the hotel and can sleep 2 adults and a child. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Executive Triple Rooms</strong> are bout 32m² and have an extra large double bed and a single bed. They sleep 3 people and are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Classic &amp; Superior Rooms for Single Use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
